<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>가나비 AI — 일본어 수행평가 생성기</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #f5f2e8;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --green-light: #c8ddb0;
    --green-dark: #5a8a3c;
    --green-btn: #c8ddb0;
    --green-text: #4a7a32;
    --text: #2d2d2d;
    --text-light: #666;
    --border: #d0c9b0;
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }

  .screen { display: none; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 40px 20px; }
  .screen.active { display: flex; }

  .logo-area { margin-bottom: 28px; text-align: center; }
  .logo-tagline { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--green-dark); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }

  /* 카드 스타일 */
  .settings-card, .upload-card { background: var(--card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); width: 100%; max-width: 600px; }

  /* 버튼 스타일 */
  .btn-primary { background: var(--green-btn); color: var(--green-text); border: none; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; margin-top: 10px; }
  .btn-secondary { background: white; color: var(--green-text); border: 2px solid var(--green-btn); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; margin-top: 10px; }
  
  /* AI 리포트 스타일 */
  #ai-report-area { display: none; margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #fff9e6; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #ffe082; text-align: left; }
  .ai-badge { background: #f57c00; color: white; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 5px; }

  /* 행 선택 버튼 */
  .row-btn-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
  .row-btn { padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 20px; border: 2px solid #eee; background: white; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; }
  .row-btn.selected { border-color: var(--green-dark); background: var(--green-btn); color: var(--green-text); }

  /* 2번 문제 그리드 */
  .word-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .word-card { border: 2px solid var(--green-light); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; background: #f9fdf5; }

  /* 테스트 출력용 */
  #test-screen { background: white; width: 100%; min-height: 100vh; padding: 50px; display: none; }
  .test-title { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .q-block { margin-bottom: 30px; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="select-screen" class="screen active">
  <div class="logo-area">
    <div class="logo-mark"><span class="logo-tagline">가나비 AI</span></div>
    <p>AI가 분석하는 지능형 일본어 평가 생성기</p>
  </div>
  <div class="settings-card" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">평가할 문자를 선택하세요</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px;">
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="selectScript('hiragana')">히라가나 (あ)</button>
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="selectScript('katakana')">가타카나 (ア)</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="settings-screen" class="screen">
  <div class="settings-card">
    <h2 id="settings-title">히라가나 설정</h2>
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">1번 문제: 출제할 행을 선택하세요 (최소 1개)</p>
    <div class="row-btn-group" id="row-btns"></div>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 20px;">2번 문제: 난이도별 단어 수</p>
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; margin: 15px 0;">
      <div>상: <input type="number" id="cnt-sang" value="1" min="0" max="5" style="width: 40px;"></div>
      <div>중: <input type="number" id="cnt-jung" value="2" min="0" max="5" style="width: 40px;"></div>
      <div>하: <input type="number" id="cnt-ha" value="1" min="0" max="5" style="width: 40px;"></div>
    </div>

    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="showScreen('upload-screen')">다음: 파일 업로드</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="upload-screen" class="screen">
  <div class="upload-card">
    <h2>📋 엑셀 파일 업로드</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-bottom: 15px;">A열: 상 / B열: 중 / C열: 하 (한국어 명사 입력)</p>
    
    <div id="drop-zone" style="border: 2px dashed var(--green-light); padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; cursor: pointer; background: #f9fdf5;" onclick="document.getElementById('file-input').click()">
      <p>📂 파일을 여기에 끌어다 놓거나 클릭하세요</p>
      <input type="file" id="file-input" accept=".xlsx, .xls" style="display: none;" onchange="handleFileUpload(this)">
    </div>

    <div id="ai-report-area">
      <h3 style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #f57c00;"><span class="ai-badge">AI 검수</span> 난이도 분석 결과</h3>
      <div id="ai-feedback-list" style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;"></div>
      <button class="btn-primary" style="background: #f57c00; color: white; padding: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;" onclick="applyAI()">AI 추천 난이도로 자동 교정하기</button>
    </div>

    <button class="btn-primary" id="generate-btn" disabled onclick="generateTest()">시험지 생성하기</button>
    <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="showScreen('settings-screen')">이전으로</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="test-screen">
  <div class="test-title" id="out-test-title">일본어 쓰기 수행평가</div>
  <div class="q-block">
    <p>1. 다음 <span id="out-q1-rows" style="font-weight: bold; color: var(--green-dark);"></span> 에 해당하는 문자를 쓰시오.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="q-block">
    <p>2. 다음 단어에 해당하는 일본어를 쓰시오.</p>
    <div class="word-grid" id="out-word-grid"></div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="location.reload()">다시 만들기</button>
</div>

<script>
// ── 데이터베이스 (대회용 샘플 데이터) ──
const wordDB = {
  "병원": { kana: "びょういん", level: "상" },
  "학교": { kana: "がっこう", level: "상" },
  "도서관": { kana: "としょかん", level: "상" },
  "우체국": { kana: "ゆうびんきょく", level: "상" },
  "고등학교": { kana: "こうとうがっこう", level: "상" },
  "모자": { kana: "ぼうし", level: "중" },
  "우표": { kana: "きって", level: "중" },
  "수학": { kana: "すうがく", level: "중" },
  "공원": { kana: "こうえん", level: "중" },
  "오후": { kana: "ごご", level: "중" },
  "가방": { kana: "かばん", level: "하" },
  "책": { kana: "ほん", level: "하" },
  "의자": { kana: "いす", level: "하" },
  "창문": { kana: "まど", level: "하" },
  "산책": { kana: "さんぽ", level: "중" }, // 박수 분석에 의해 중으로 유도됨
  "책상": { kana: "つくえ", level: "하" }
};

let currentScript = 'hiragana';
let selectedRows = [];
let uploadedWords = { sang: [], jung: [], ha: [] };

function showScreen(id) {
  document.querySelectorAll('.screen').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
  document.getElementById('test-screen').style.display = 'none';
  document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
}

function selectScript(type) {
  currentScript = type;
  document.getElementById('settings-title').textContent = type === 'hiragana' ? '히라가나 설정' : '가타카나 설정';
  const rows = ['아행', '카행', '사행', '타행', '나행', '하행', '마행', '라행', '야행+와행'];
  const btnGroup = document.getElementById('row-btns');
  btnGroup.innerHTML = rows.map(r => `<button class="row-btn" onclick="toggleRow(this, '${r}')">${r}</button>`).join('');
  showScreen('settings-screen');
}

function toggleRow(btn, row) {
  btn.classList.toggle('selected');
  if (btn.classList.contains('selected')) selectedRows.push(row);
  else selectedRows = selectedRows.filter(r => r !== row);
}

// ── AI 검수 엔진 ──
function getMora(kana) {
  return kana.replace(/[ゃゅょャュョ]/g, "").length; // 요음 제외 박수 계산
}

function handleFileUpload(input) {
  const file = input.files[0];
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(e) {
    const data = new Uint8Array(e.target.result);
    const workbook = XLSX.read(data, { type: 'array' });
    const sheet = workbook.Sheets[workbook.SheetNames[0]];
    const json = XLSX.utils.sheet_to_json(sheet, { header: 1 });

    uploadedWords = { sang: [], jung: [], ha: [] };
    let feedbackHTML = "";
    let issuesFound = false;

    // 엑셀 파싱 (1행은 제목이라 가정하고 1부터 시작)
    for (let i = 1; i < json.length; i++) {
      const [s, j, h] = json[i];
      if (s) checkAI(s, "상");
      if (j) checkAI(j, "중");
      if (h) checkAI(h, "하");
    }

    function checkAI(word, userLevel) {
      const dbInfo = wordDB[word];
      if (dbInfo) {
        const mora = getMora(dbInfo.kana);
        let aiLevel = "하";
        if (mora >= 4) aiLevel = "상";
        else if (mora === 3) aiLevel = "중";

        if (aiLevel !== userLevel) {
          issuesFound = true;
          feedbackHTML += `<div>• <b>${word}</b>: 선생님은 [${userLevel}]이라 하셨지만, AI 분석 결과 <b>${mora}박자</b>이므로 <b>[${aiLevel}]</b>을 추천합니다.</div>`;
          uploadedWords[aiLevel.toLowerCase()].push(word); // AI 추천으로 일단 분류
        } else {
          uploadedWords[userLevel.toLowerCase()].push(word);
        }
      } else {
        // DB에 없는 단어는 일단 유저 분류 유지
        uploadedWords[userLevel.toLowerCase()].push(word);
      }
    }

    if (issuesFound) {
      document.getElementById('ai-report-area').style.display = 'block';
      document.getElementById('ai-feedback-list').innerHTML = feedbackHTML;
    } else {
      document.getElementById('ai-report-area').style.display = 'block';
      document.getElementById('ai-feedback-list').innerHTML = "✅ 모든 단어의 박자 난이도가 적절합니다.";
    }
    document.getElementById('generate-btn').disabled = false;
  };
  reader.readAsArrayBuffer(file);
}

function applyAI() {
  alert("AI 추천 난이도가 적용되었습니다.");
  document.getElementById('ai-report-area').style.background = "#e8f5e0";
  document.getElementById('ai-report-area').style.borderColor = "#4a8a3a";
}

function generateTest() {
  document.querySelectorAll('.screen').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
  document.getElementById('test-screen').style.display = 'block';

  document.getElementById('out-test-title').textContent = currentScript === 'hiragana' ? '히라가나 쓰기 수행평가' : '가타카나 쓰기 수행평가';
  document.getElementById('out-q1-rows').textContent = selectedRows.join(', ');

  const grid = document.getElementById('out-word-grid');
  grid.innerHTML = "";

  // 난이도별 설정된 개수만큼 랜덤 추출
  const sCnt = document.getElementById('cnt-sang').value;
  const jCnt = document.getElementById('cnt-jung').value;
  const hCnt = document.getElementById('cnt-ha').value;

  const finalWords = [
    ...uploadedWords.sang.sort(() => 0.5 - Math.random()).slice(0, sCnt),
    ...uploadedWords.jung.sort(() => 0.5 - Math.random()).slice(0, jCnt),
    ...uploadedWords.ha.sort(() => 0.5 - Math.random()).slice(0, hCnt)
  ];

  finalWords.forEach((w, idx) => {
    grid.innerHTML += `<div class="word-card">(${idx + 1}) ${w}</div>`;
  });
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
